{"type": "article", "id": 22872, "title": "明星都爱的墨镜红牌 Gentle Monster ，店铺也很迷人", "description": "一定得去店里看看啊！", "date": "2016-02-26T12:12:03Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 8238, "name": "墨镜"}, {"id": 620, "name": "韩国"}, {"id": 610, "name": "明星"}, {"id": 1451, "name": "韩剧"}, {"id": 7227, "name": "街拍"}, {"id": 3000, "name": "店铺设计"}, {"id": 141, "name": "展览"}, {"id": 24006, "name": "HBA"}, {"id": 24007, "name": "Gentle Monster"}], "category": 19, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 334, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702144608w7Jtm42gfcIaAPKv.png", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">当你看到别人戴墨镜都有型有款，自己戴却很像要去拉《二泉映月》，也许你应该试试更适合亚洲人脸型的设计，比如<a href=\"http://en.gentlemonster.com\">韩国品牌 Gentle Monster</a>。</p>\n<p class=\"\">这个 2011 年才成立的品牌，近两年来有多火呢？像是全智贤、BigBang 的 GD、李敏镐、金宇彬、玄彬、尹恩惠等等韩流明星都在出演的电视剧里、街拍照片里戴过它家的墨镜。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144553OSTAyQWKHmx7oRlV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.46601942\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144553b6SxOuqkXMvYz8JN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.33783784\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144553elnJHvK29uCB1xgQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144554qxJ8AdCg4Z9INEPQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68454259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144554sWSJqRc9NHA2LbZi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69246032\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">几款经典的复古造型非常具有辨识度，并且大多 Gentle Monster 的墨镜在镜架侧面都有品牌的 logo，远远看上去像是个小 V 字。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144555ejk26dRgX7TVCxhS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.83333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021445553FsWSJzTB8n9palc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59521095\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">除了受到各路明星的喜爱之外，也和一些时装品牌有过合作，比如 Opening Ceremony 2016 年春夏和秋冬系列在纽约时装周的走秀，模特戴的眼镜都是来自  Gentle Monster 为其设计的特别款。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144556g3aJ5zsmDueQnY7K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72826087\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">以及 HBA（Hood by Air ）同在纽约时装周亮相的 2016 年春夏系列。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144556eyXS39JsmLtCpbij.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70795107\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">不过，相信早在韩剧《来自星星的你》大火之际，应该已经有不少粉丝跑去买了千颂依同款，这个品牌的墨镜好看且价格亲民（大多在 250 美元左右）这里就不多说了。</p>\n<p class=\"\">因为他家的店铺也实在是很迷人啊。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\">目前在韩国有五家旗舰店，各自有独特的主题，比如第一家 “THE KITCHEN” 就是在一个古旧的餐厅里，从内到外的断壁残垣最大程度保留了建筑物原本的样子，怎么看都像是吸血鬼电影里神秘的古堡。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144557Ohpgw0cQd69SU8lV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144557RVUBMYWL2jq4uKsa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144558G3JFa1qORKiX59kH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">各式各样的厨房用具、古董钢琴，几乎没有任何“这是家眼镜店哦”的迹象，类似玩一场寻宝游戏的感觉。即使是正经陈列一面墙的角落，也比一般的眼镜店有艺术感多了。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144559ta04CyXqVRmG1PLd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">还有以“船”为主题的：</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144559qtNzV0KdXMrcA9va.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021446005fscLrQBqy31EZdD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">“BATHHOUSE”是由旧澡堂改成的，斑驳的马赛克瓷砖还依稀可见：</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144600wWg5HQn2OGSlAv81.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021446011HSyUegFwIo4rqvY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021446010hK47wcpCVIbzuOF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144602lgud6IzoF3jTJU1f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144602BwKW8hbn43C9OaIX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">最新的两家更是越来越酷炫，“HOME AND RECOVERY”（家&amp;治愈）大概想表达家是最后的庇护所，将不同复古的房间变成了品牌的 showroom。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144603THl2iQwGYhR4FfZD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021446038cpt9eUaAuhxwVNX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144604xesLXcVrtFOq5oZH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144604FEljGvxnNY9mSaCM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144605AIeJ3yPhWil6rqQt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"> “THE PLAY”则是与戏剧艺术有关：</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144605lcuLb4nZs6CERtqo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64351852\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144606L5s87Eo21rAkjDOe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144607K8dpLRaHM1f9JsZY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144607PXZHmKVYDr2dGCtB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.22685185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">这么酷的品牌，背后的人物却很低调。关于创始人兼创意总监 Hankook Kim 的消息很少。只知道在创立 Gentle Monster 之前，他在一家英语培训机构工作。平日里痴迷于收藏古董眼镜，后来和几位朋友开始设计更适合韩国人的复古墨镜，在细节上精雕细琢，店铺设计上天马行空（不惜血本），实在不容错过。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144608CXDFdofHEaQJjBhn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66477273\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></figure>\n\n"}